lead_paragraph: Renault should give up on this year's Formula One car and focus on designing a better one for 2017, the team's Danish driver Kevin Magnussen said on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Motor Racing: Magnussen Says Renault Should Focus on 2017 Car
